{"author":"Joe Oakhart","author_email":"joeoakhart+bot@navapbc.com","author_id":"594c-9dcf-5ad6-4e6d","author_sig":"{\"payload\": \"\", \"payloadType\": \"application/vnd.rebar.authorship.v1+json\", \"signatures\": [{\"keyid\": \"594c-9dcf-5ad6-4e6d\", \"sig\": \"\"}]}","data":{"content_hash":"2114da51b2b2caaf4e0e5f12492a35fbfa8ef5de2d103d14404af80fa295113f","digest":{"component_or_area":"SNAPSHOT compaction and provenance projection","key_entities":["creation_channel","creation_channel_inferred","SNAPSHOT.data.compiled_state","src/rebar/_commands/compact.py","src/rebar/_commands/fsck.py","src/rebar/reducer/_processors.py","_snapshot_strip_keys()","_project_legacy_creation_channel()","process_snapshot","rebuild_snapshot_from_full_log","fsck --repair-snapshots","include_retired=True","docs/output-schemas.md","docs/event-schema.md","docs/concurrency.md","SNAPSHOT_STALE_CHANNEL"],"problem_keywords":["creation provenance","snapshot compaction","creation_channel","inferred marker","legacy snapshot migration","snapshot rebuild","full-log replay","rollback recovery","fsck repair","horizon compaction"],"propositions":["Creation provenance must survive SNAPSHOT compaction so recorded, inferred, and unknown channels stay auditable across normal, horizon, snapshot-only, legacy, and rebuild paths.","creation_channel and the true-only creation_channel_inferred marker are stored inside compiled_state, never on the SNAPSHOT envelope, and are never stripped by _snapshot_strip_keys().","process_snapshot calls _project_legacy_creation_channel to re-evaluate absent, None, or provisional-unknown state into deterministic jira/unknown while passing through concrete recorded and already-inferred channels.","Inferred historical Jira tickets materialize creation_channel=jira with creation_channel_inferred=true so snapshot-only replay retains the marker without retired CREATE files.","Old-code compaction may omit the field but the CREATE is retained as .retired, so rebuild from full log with include_retired=True and fsck --repair-snapshots recover the channel.","Documentation must state genesis provenance lives in compiled_state distinct from SNAPSHOT authorship and that full-log, snapshot-only, and rebuilt replay emit identical channel values."]},"digest_hash_version":1,"model":"claude-opus-4-8","schema":"ticket_digest_v1"},"env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","event_type":"TICKET_DIGEST","timestamp":1784313929566982001,"uuid":"dea17164-276d-4c5c-b7f2-8f75c54fe0d2"}